nginx-gone (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * gone on|off directive for per-context enable/disable
  * gone_map_file directive for loading URI list from file
  * gone_use_request_uri directive for matching $request_uri
  * Exact URI matching via hash table
  * PCRE regex matching (case-sensitive and case-insensitive)
  * Server rewrite phase handler for early interception

 -- Rumen Damyanov <contact@rumenx.com>  Sun, 30 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0300
